(8, 'Matt Stewart', 31966, 'W', 2, '\"Within every angel is a spirit of light that will fight as long as there is darkness.\"', 0, '{W}{W}', 2, 'cc92be07-1f83-55ce-90c7-3cabd7fd7634', 466762, 'Bishop of Wings', 1, 2.31, 'rare', 'Whenever an Angel enters the battlefield under your control, you gain 4 life.\r\nWhenever an Angel you control dies, create a 1/1 white Spirit creature token with flying.', 227, 'Human,Cleric', 4, 'Creature'),
