(315, 'Lie Setiawan', 32274, 'U', 2, 'The merfolk know every contour of their coral homes; each reef is a garden in times of peace, and a refuge and fortress in times of war.', 0, '{1}{U}', 2, 'e5d2a34d-9f63-57b1-a76a-cd26099e76e9', 469868, 'Coral Merfolk', 2, 0.27, 'common', '', 227, 'Merfolk', 1, 'Creature'),
